"program will be hidden to the notification area if the notification area "
"icon is enabled, or minimized if the icon is disabled."
msgstr ""
"{app_name} starter automatisk når du logger deg på systemet. Programmet "
"skjules i systemfeltet hvis ikonet for systemfeltet er aktivert eller "
"minimeres hvis ikonet er deaktivert."

#: src/ui/qt/main_window.cpp
msgid ""
"{app_name} will automatically check for updates at startup, but no more "
"often than once every {count} day"
msgid_plural ""
"{app_name} will automatically check for updates at startup, but no more "
"often than once every {count} days"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/ui/qt/main_window.cpp
msgid "Please install languages"
msgstr "Installer språk"

#: src/ui/qt/main_window.cpp
msgid "Please select languages"
msgstr "Velg språk"

#: src/ui/qt/main_window.cpp
msgid "Please select actions"
msgstr "Velg handlinger"

#: src/ui/qt/main_window.cpp
msgid "Press {hotkey} to start area selection"
msgstr "Trykk {hotkey} for å starte områdevalg"

#: src/ui/qt/main_window.cpp
